cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS

This paper proposes a quantization scheme for efficient on-device inference of deep learning models, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses a co-design training procedure, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed scheme involves integer-only arithmetic, which is related to numerical analysis (cs.NE). Finally, the experiments are conducted on popular CPUs, which is relevant to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DS).
